title: Phase One Capture One Pro 11.3.0.20
description:
Phase One Capture One PRO 13 is one of the best professional digital photo converters in RAW format. It supports a wide range of modern cameras (Canon, Nikon, Epson, Fuji, Konica Minolta, Leica, Mamiya, Olympus, Pentax, Sony) the latest models, and provides the conversion of raw images in RAW format into readable formats JPEG, TIFF, PNG, DNG, etc.
Capture One allows you to use several options for adjusting the same image. As a template, the original RAW is used, not the result of previous adjustments. The workspace is divided into several areas. Their number is equal to the number of processing options for the original digital negative. Adjusting the white balance is performed using the color temperature and tint controls. In addition, you can select the scene programs that are traditional for many cameras. You can also use the pipette. The photograph shows a neutral gray dot from which the white balance is built
